{"tid":963465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NowTV 首試 4K HDR 本地直播除夕倒數煙花","createTime":"2018-12-31T14:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T16:37:49.000Z","uid":37554,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"46ebfec378e086911b42266f882c95616321bf67","tid":963465,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"2018 年即將過去，收費電視台 Now TV 今日就宣佈繼今年 6 月的俄羅斯世界盃之後，再提供 4K HDR 直播節目，今次更屬本地製作，說的就是將在 12 月 31 日除夕晚於維港兩旁舉行的除夕倒數儀式及煙花匯演。<br />\n<br />\nNow TV 當晚 11 時起將於 Now 331 直播台全程直播除夕例數活動，而在晚上 11:55 倒數儀式及煙花匯演舉行前，特設的 4K 頻道「Now 330 台」就會開始同步直播，訊號解像度將為 3,840 x 2,160，並採用 HEVC 編碼、每秒 50 格幀率（FPS）、10bit 色深及 HLG HDR 高動應範圍訊號規格，與世界盃時的直播賽事看齊。<br />\n<br />\n要收看今次香港首場 4K HDR 煙花匯演直播，Now TV 用戶必須已選用指定 4K 接駁服務、配備 Now One 4K UHD 全功能機頂盒並以網上行光纖寬頻連接，再配合支援直通傳輸或接收 4K HLG HDR 訊號之影音裝置，需求與觀看世界盃 4K HDR 賽事時一模一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/4k1-694x521.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F4k1-694x521.png&h=119a90aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/4k2-694x521.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F4k2-694x521.png&h=38522458&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9575b06164f377e636f7707c3e7b6c9ad21572f4","tid":963465,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"659df261cb73b9389760b10cddd3502c0bae3073","tid":963465,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘩嘩嘩，好撚高科技呀仆街！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/